fd40b55320a7b8628927dd1eb335346f","tid":935582,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56201e6f44d8c02c58ed4fd4e844814066eba1b","tid":935582,"uid":18772,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:34:27.000Z","msg":"以前索羅斯睇準攻擊香港兌換率機制從中取利<br />\n政府都屌佢<br />\n而家係大陸狗公司利用香港漏洞犯法 包括禁運國同禁運武器<br />\n大陸先係危害緊香港既敵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2ca6715f385724ed69926abf137515e8fe2478","tid":935582,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:35:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.usconsulate.gov/pr-2018121001/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.usconsulate.gov%2Fpr-2018121001%2F&d=3VF6E2gJR1D7OfX8qt8MeE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=25983f1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.usconsulate.gov/pr-2018121001/</a><br />\n<br />\nOn December 5-7, senior delegations from the U.S. Department of State and U.S. Department of Commerce met with representatives of several Hong Kong Government agencies to consider recent progress and performance in bilateral cooperation on sanctions enforcement and strategic trade controls.<br />\n<br />\nOn sanctions enforcement, the U.S. delegation took note of recent steps by Hong Kong to enact ordinances necessary to implement United Nations sanctions, and new laws making it harder to register and operate shell companies in Hong Kong. The U.S. team recommended that Hong Kong improve the flow of enforcement cooperation information, and devote additional resources to sanctions enforcement, particularly with respect to shipping activities that violate United Nations sanctions on North Korea and Iran.<br />\n<br />\nOn exports controls, the U.S. delegation sought further improvements in Hong Kong&rsquo;s tracking of strategic commodities and controlled items building on recent progress, and additional action and assistance in enforcement of restrictions on re-exports, so as to prevent diversion of such items to the development and production of weapons of mass destruction and unauthorized military end users.<br />\n<br />\nThe United States looks forward to continued close cooperation with Hong Kong on these important matters."},{"pid":"0ea5f7ea0b344afd64614f06c82c7f81a986b947","tid":935582,"uid":22554,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:36:18.000Z","msg":"WOW, 依單野比3個特區護照嚴重好多<br />\n完全係最後通牒FEEL"},{"pid":"c56934946e99676ed4bee512c97f015d0628c398","tid":935582,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:37:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 陰公豬囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889ef6682eee434a8890232834df5dda35bc0886","tid":935582,"uid":222392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係肉撚酸呀！"},{"pid":"3ba0814929d71700d347fb2d0407576e7cb296de","tid":935582,"uid":55868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T07:52:51.000Z","msg":"干預別國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654cdab3835c5862a6660855333da998e9ce5bea","tid":935582,"uid":23180,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T08:00:41.000Z","msg":"幾時拉番d美國代表換人質？<br />\n<br />\n關係法又對香港無咩著數，柒婆係時候為國家做野啦<br />\n<br /